id: pm-o34s
title: "CodeFactor/Complexity: remove 33 suppressions and split 100+ complexity-point dispatch hot spots"
description: "Broaden the active CodeFactor child into a large PR that reduces the ESLint cyclomatic-complexity baseline from 146 to 113 individual suppressions versus main, removes 9 suppressed file entries entirely, and splits the largest MCP/extension/SDK dispatch and normalization hot spots into reusable primitives. Existing related lineage remains pm-arzz/pm-zro7/pm-lzzp under pm-92if; no duplicate item created. Follow-up work remains available for the wider 113-suppression backlog."
