  "2026-06-30T22:01:43.992Z",claude-code-agent,"Progress evidence: broadened CodeFactor complexity cleanup now removes 24 tracked ESLint complexity suppressions (137 -> 113) across extension dispatch/policy/tool-schema, MCP server dispatch, bootstrap/list/registration helpers, core item-format, linked-test parser/assertions, search filters/scorer, and calendar range/filter helpers. Focused regression passed: node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/extensions/extension-command.spec.ts tests/unit/cli/main-loose-options.spec.ts tests/unit/core/extensions/extension-policy.spec.ts tests/unit/extensions/runtime-registrations.spec.ts tests/unit/sdk/action-schema-parity.spec.ts tests/unit/sdk/sdk-index.spec.ts tests/unit/core/item-format.spec.ts tests/unit/commands/search.spec.ts tests/unit/commands/calendar.spec.ts tests/unit/commands/test-command.spec.ts tests/integration/mcp-dynamic-package-actions.spec.ts (8 files, 357 tests passed)."
  "2026-06-30T22:05:08.996Z",claude-code-agent,"Manual test evidence: strict temp-dir smoke passed with sandboxed PM_PATH/PM_GLOBAL_PATH. Covered init, create with deadline, files link, linked test add/run with JSON assertion, list/search, install calendar + calendar JSON output, package init/install, generated package command, and package doctor deep. Smoke item: pm-l2gw in temporary tracker; temp directory removed."
  "2026-06-30T22:30:03.222Z",claude-code-agent,"Evidence update: complexity baseline now drops from 146 to 113 individual ESLint complexity suppressions versus main (33 removed). The PR removes 9 suppressed file entries entirely and cuts the largest MCP dispatcher from a 100+ complexity-point hotspot into handler primitives. Verification passed: pnpm typecheck; focused suites 122 tests; full coverage 262 files / 5260 tests at 100/100/100/100; pnpm lint; pnpm contracts:check; pnpm quality:docs-links; pnpm security:scan; pnpm audit --audit-level low; pnpm changelog:pm:check with pm-changelog 2026.6.30 and unchanged CHANGELOG.md; Sentry/telemetry gate ok with 0 critical/high Sentry issues and telemetry finish_error_rate_pct 0.77; release:gates passed through build/typecheck/docs/static/full coverage/version/security/npx smoke/package-first dogfood and stopped only at Greptile because changes were not committed yet. Greptile will be rerun after commit and before push."
  "2026-06-30T22:36:54.977Z",claude-code-agent,"Greptile pre-push review evidence: greptile review --branch main --agent completed as review 21a5b4f0-110a-4cda-9dfa-a7f808ebe33b with Confidence 5/5 and no review comments. Summary confirmed extension/MCP dispatch tables and extracted item-format/policy helpers preserve behavior."
  "2026-06-30T23:00:42.471Z",claude-code-agent,"Gemini review fix evidence: guarded extension policy normalization for settings objects that omit extensions, extended tests/unit/core/extensions/extension-policy.spec.ts to cover missing settings.extensions, and reran pnpm typecheck, focused extension-policy test, full coverage (262 files/5260 tests, 100/100/100/100), and pnpm lint/static-quality successfully on the patched head."
  "2026-06-30T23:27:39.091Z",claude-code-agent,"Review response evidence: addressed current PR review findings by removing the unsafe bootstrap list-flag cast, preserving warn-mode unknown-field callbacks during direct normalization, pruning undefined optional linked-test/test-run fields, validating plan step status/order inputs, guarding MCP handler dispatch with own-key lookups, limiting schema inference to schema add-type, and preserving legacy MCP integer-prefix parsing for reorder inputs. Verification passed after the final patch: pnpm typecheck; node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/cli/bootstrap-args.spec.ts tests/unit/core/item/item-format-internal.spec.ts tests/unit/mcp/mcp-server-branch-residual.spec.ts tests/integration/mcp-dynamic-package-actions.spec.ts; node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/core/item/item-format-validation.spec.ts tests/unit/core/item/item-record.spec.ts tests/unit/core/item/item-format-internal.spec.ts; node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage (262 files, 5261 tests, 100/100/100/100); pnpm lint (ESLint, jscpd threshold, static quality gate)."
  "2026-06-30T23:48:30.538Z",claude-code-agent,"Review response evidence: verified Greptile warn-mode unknown-field finding against current code and added explicit canonicalDocument regression coverage for unknown_field_policy=warn so both direct normalization and canonicalization paths assert item_unknown_schema_fields warnings. Verification passed: node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/core/item/item-format-internal.spec.ts; pnpm typecheck; pnpm lint; node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage (262 files, 5262 tests, 100/100/100/100)."
  "2026-07-01T00:07:42.767Z",claude-code-agent,"Review response evidence: addressed current-head Gemini security/robustness findings and Greptile numeric reorder compatibility. Production changes now skip unsafe __proto__/constructor/prototype keys in front-matter and CLI unknown-option copying, guard malformed event/test arrays and nested linked-test records/lists, and preserve MCP plan reorder parseInt-style behavior for numeric fractional inputs. Verification passed: node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/core/item/item-format-internal.spec.ts tests/unit/cli/registration-helpers.spec.ts tests/unit/mcp/mcp-server-branch-residual.spec.ts; pnpm typecheck; pnpm lint; node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage (262 files, 5264 tests, 100/100/100/100)."
